text:
Buket Gülübay (born 28 February 1999) is a Turkish volleyball player.
She played at the 2015 Girls' Youth European Volleyball Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship.
She played for VakıfBank S.K.
